data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Slatington! Nestled in a peaceful neighborhood on a corner lot this charming 2 BR, 2 bath ranch is the epitome of comfort and style. Step outside to the enclosed deck, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee. The large 2C garage is a game-changer. Not only does it provide shelter for your vehicles, but it also offers plenty of room for all your storage needs. As you step inside, be prepared to be impressed by the meticulous renovations that grace every corner of this home. Recent carpeting in the BRs adds a touch of luxury and warmth underfoot, creating a cozy atmosphere throughout. Tons of cabinets in the kitchen! Venture into the fully fin basement and discover a world of possibilities. Complete with a 2nd full bath, a spacious family room, and a convenient laundry room, this lower level is a versatile space ready to accommodate your lifestyle. Whether you envision it as a home theater, a playroom, or a home gym, the options are endless.
